{"tid":1846031,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高鐵西九站外判員工疑發燒入院　等候化驗結果","createTime":"2020-01-27T12:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T13:13:34.000Z","uid":5195,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3445570e7e26dca05c1052fd88f17dc5413a4555","tid":1846031,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"據了解，一名在高鐵西九龍站工作的港鐵外判公司職員，因身體不適懷疑發燒往急症室求醫，已被隔離和等候檢查結果。港鐵提醒內部員工注意個人衛生、配帶防護衣，留意身體狀況，車站會安排相關環境的消毒工作。<br />\n《香港01》致電涉事外判公司國際永勝行政總裁蔡明輝查詢，他證實本周有西九高鐵站員工發燒或不適請病假，惟至今未有得悉從事高鐵西九龍站的員工，出現任何懷疑或確診武漢肺炎個案。<br />\n《香港01》已就事件向港鐵查詢，尚待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856cab50eefc750420ea8ca01e1592ec5ae19e3b","tid":1846031,"uid":161261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:41:42.000Z","msg":"恭喜支鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b5d1b77af22b9eb8928afaf10b11199e97f305","tid":1846031,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a872797d3fb23962b5f9ebdaa370d4ae60b2fd0","tid":1846031,"uid":45123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"非密切接觸都奶野 癡線"},{"pid":"51e80cd8fb8bd3599efa044626bfe9db346ed339","tid":1846031,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"得返一日時間 一句講晒  1.29罷工加黎明行動 做定唔做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846030</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f9737fa355826f69698db6e0a4a54f3acd31546","tid":1846031,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7354ae3f6532020fc90f9e5c3a5a622e152ae61e","tid":1846031,"uid":259